ON THE ROAD, ALL RIGHT?

12:42.888 --> 12:45.098
- NO, WE MUST WAIT
UNTIL YOUR FATHER GETS HERE.

12:45.098 --> 12:46.641
- HE DOESN'T GIVE A SHIT
ABOUT THE CEREMONY, TRUST ME.

12:46.641 --> 12:47.977
