12:52.982 --> 12:54.232
- GOD, THAT IS SO SICK.

12:54.232 --> 12:55.818
ARE YOU GONNA START
BANGING HIM AGAIN TOO?

12:55.818 --> 12:57.987
- UH, I'M SORRY,
