13:40.153 --> 13:42.864
THROUGH THIS BAPTISM,
YEVGENY IS CLEANSED FROM SIN

13:42.864 --> 13:47.912
TO A NEW BIRTH TO INNOCENCE
BY WATER AND THE HOLY SPIRIT.

