WE HAVE ENOUGH STUFF ALREADY?

14:03.551 --> 14:05.888
- NO.
I HAVE SEVEN SIBLINGS.

14:05.888 --> 14:07.681
I NEED SOMETHING
FOR ALL OF THEM.

14:07.681 --> 14:09.557
TIP IT A LITTLE MORE.

14:11.351 --> 14:12.978
FIRE IN THE HOLE.

14:15.563 --> 14:17.691
- I'M GONNA GO VISIT MY FATHER
IN THE HOSPITAL NOW.

14:17.691 --> 14:19.859
YOU WANT TO COME?
- CAN'T.

14:19.859 --> 14:22.946
GOT TO HEAD BACK TO THE VAN.
