14:22.946 --> 14:25.824
I NEED TO GO CHECK ON HIM.
- YOU SHOULD COME LIVE WITH ME.

14:25.824 --> 14:27.450
- I CAN'T LEAVE
THE OTHER KIDS.

14:27.450 --> 14:29.119
- THEY CAN COME LIVE
WITH US TOO.

14:30.913 --> 14:32.872
- OKAY.

14:38.044 --> 14:40.672
CARL.

14:40.672 --> 14:42.549
- YEAH, I KNOW.

14:43.633 --> 14:46.553
- SO PIN HIS SKIN TO THE FELT.

14:46.553 --> 14:48.097
- MM-HMM.

14:48.097 --> 14:49.014
- GOOD JOB.

14:49.014 --> 14:50.265
- EW, I CAN'T LOOK.

14:50.265 --> 14:52.017
- THIS IS FUN.
- ISN'T IT?

14:53.727 --> 14:56.229
- SPEAKING OF FUN...

14:56.229 --> 14:58.898
MY PARENTS AREN'T GONNA BE
HOME THIS WEEKEND.

14:58.898 --> 15:01.110
YOU SHOULD COME OVER,
AND WE CAN WATCH PORN.

15:01.110 --> 15:02.861
I DOWNLOADED
SPERMS OF ENDEARMENT.

15:02.861 --> 15:06.031
- [laughs]
I'M NOT REALLY INTO PORN.

15:06.031 --> 15:07.490
- ME EITHER.

15:07.490 --> 15:08.992
- YEAH, IT'S GROSS, RIGHT?
- UGH.

15:08.992 --> 15:10.910
- YOU KNOW, THEY'RE LIKE,
"OH, YEAH."

15:10.910 --> 15:12.495
- "OH, GIVE IT TO ME."
- "OH, YEAH."

15:12.495 --> 15:13.956
- "JUST LIKE THAT."

15:13.956 --> 15:15.832
[both laugh]

15:15.832 --> 15:17.625
[chuckles]

15:17.625 --> 15:19.210
- HEY, UM, LOOK AT THIS.

15:19.210 --> 15:21.046
HERE'S HIS LUNGS.

15:21.046 --> 15:21.838
- COOL.

15:21.838 --> 15:23.048
- AND HERE'S HIS SPLEEN.

15:23.048 --> 15:24.049
- HMM.

15:24.049 --> 15:25.425
- AND...

15:27.052 --> 15:28.470
THIS IS HIS HEART.

15:33.058 --> 15:34.017
- FOR ME?

15:34.017 --> 15:35.435
- [chuckles]

15:37.187 --> 15:39.064
- GIVE ME A FUCKING BREAK.

15:39.064 --> 15:42.525
[slow rock music]

15:42.525 --> 15:50.617
