16:02.045 --> 16:03.713
- OFF THE BUS, SINGLE LINE.

16:03.713 --> 16:06.175
NO TALKING, NO PUSHING.

16:21.439 --> 16:23.108
KEEP THE LINE MOVING.

16:32.700 --> 16:36.371
- IF THERE ARE FOUR ACES
IN A DECK OF CARDS,

16:36.371 --> 16:39.208
THEN THE PROBABILITY
