17:08.112 --> 17:10.029
- MAY I CONTINUE?

17:10.029 --> 17:12.241
- DON'T EVER SAY
I'M NOT A MAN OF MY WORD AGAIN.

17:12.241 --> 17:14.201
- IF WE DON'T RETURN
OUR ACE TO THE DECK,

17:14.201 --> 17:16.161
THEN THE PROBABILITY
OF CHOOSING A SECOND ACE...

17:16.161 --> 17:18.329
- JUMP ON YOUR RIGHT FOOT.
