PAUSE.

17:19.956 --> 17:21.040
- HIGH KNEES.

17:21.040 --> 17:23.042
- HIGH KNEES.
INTERESTING.

17:23.042 --> 17:25.545
- I'M NOT SURE ALL THIS WOO-WOO
SPIRITUAL STUFF

17:25.545 --> 17:27.046
IS GONNA HELP DAD.

17:27.046 --> 17:28.798
- NOT WITH THAT ATTITUDE,
IT WON'T.

17:28.798 --> 17:32.886
- I'M HAVING A GREAT TIME.
- OH, YAY!

17:32.886 --> 17:34.053
- WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU GUYS DOING?

17:34.053 --> 17:36.639
- WE'RE WAKING FRANK'S SPIRIT.

17:36.639 --> 17:38.016
- WHY DON'T YOU JUST DO THIS?

17:38.016 --> 17:40.560
- WHAT HAPPENED?

17:40.560 --> 17:43.188
- [gasping]

17:43.188 --> 17:45.064
HE'S AWAKE!

17:45.064 --> 17:46.691
