17:48.359 --> 17:50.111
DAD, ARE YOU OKAY?

17:50.111 --> 17:51.571
- WHERE AM I, DEBBIE?

17:51.571 --> 17:53.072
- DEBBIE?

17:53.072 --> 17:54.824
IT--I'M SAMMI.

17:54.824 --> 17:56.451
