- HER HYMEN.

19:16.239 --> 19:17.615
- BUT LOOK AT HER.

19:17.615 --> 19:19.284
HE'S AN 11TH GRADER.

19:19.284 --> 19:20.243
SHE'S A REDHEAD.

19:20.243 --> 19:22.412
- I LOVE REDHEADS.

19:22.412 --> 19:24.331
- GOOD THING I DIDN'T
DYE MY HAIR LAST NIGHT.

19:24.331 --> 19:26.208
[both chuckle]

