20:37.654 --> 20:39.030
- HOWDY DOODY.

20:40.615 --> 20:42.451
TELL HIM TO LEAVE, OR I WILL.

20:42.451 --> 20:44.453
- ALL RIGHT, FINE.

20:47.955 --> 20:50.833
LOOK, SVETLANA WANTS YOU TO GO.

