21:47.014 --> 21:48.015
- YEAH, HUH?

21:48.015 --> 21:49.476
HELLO, HONEY.

21:49.476 --> 21:52.521
- LOOK AT SCARED LITTLE BOY
RUNNING TO DADDY.

21:52.521 --> 21:54.147
- EAT ME.

21:54.147 --> 21:55.982
- WHERE'S THIS GRANDSON OF MINE
I KEEP HEARING ABOUT?

21:55.982 --> 21:57.817
- HEY.
