22:41.819 --> 22:43.196
LET'S TRY.

22:43.196 --> 22:45.031
LET'S TRY, HUH?

22:45.031 --> 22:47.241
LET'S SEE.

22:47.241 --> 22:49.536
ALL RIGHT, HERE WE GO.
READY?

22:49.536 --> 22:50.453
SMILE.

22:50.453 --> 22:51.662
[camera shutter clicks]

22:51.662 --> 22:53.539
THAT'S NOT BAD, HUH?

22:53.539 --> 22:55.416
THAT'S PRETTY GOOD.

22:55.416 --> 22:57.586
ALL RIGHT.

22:57.586 --> 22:59.796
UH, YO.

22:59.796 --> 23:01.589
HOPEFULLY YOU GET THIS.

23:01.589 --> 23:04.050
UH, HOW'S THE POKEY, HUH?

23:04.050 --> 23:07.136
