OFF FOR ME TOO?

23:35.414 --> 23:38.334
ALL RIGHT. GOOD BOY.
BE RIGHT BACK.

24:03.568 --> 24:05.570
[both sighing]

24:07.071 --> 24:09.240
- WHAT?

24:09.240 --> 24:10.950
- NOTHING.

24:10.950 --> 24:11.951
I LIKE YOU.

24:11.951 --> 24:13.578
- [chuckles]

24:13.578 --> 24:14.996
ME TOO.

24:24.881 --> 24:27.300
I DON'T--
I DON'T THINK WE SHOULD.

24:27.300 --> 24:28.593
- WHY NOT?

24:28.593 --> 24:32.013
- I MEAN, WE JUST MET.

24:32.013 --> 24:33.848
- YOU'RE RIGHT.

24:33.848 --> 24:36.684
MAYBE WE SHOULD, UH--
I DON'T KNOW--

24:36.684 --> 24:38.019
WAIT TILL THE DANCE.

24:39.604 --> 24:41.731
- YOU'RE ASKING ME
TO THE DANCE?

24:41.731 --> 24:43.774
- [chuckles] I DON'T KNOW.
I MEAN, IF YOU'LL GO WITH ME.

24:43.774 --> 24:46.110
- [chuckles]
YEAH!

24:49.573 --> 24:50.698
- SURPRISE!

24:50.698 --> 24:53.660
all:
SURPRISE!

24:53.660 --> 24:55.036
- SEEMA?

24:55.036 --> 24:56.621
- I SEE YOU'VE MET
MY STEPBROTHER, HENRY.

24:58.539 --> 24:59.832
- STEPBROTHER?

25:02.627 --> 25:04.503
WHY WOULD YOU DO THIS TO ME?

25:04.503 --> 25:07.006
- SEEMA GAVE ME 50 BUCKS.

25:12.679 --> 25:15.514
[all laughing]

25:18.351 --> 25:20.937
- I CALL DIBS ON THE REMOTE!
- FUCK.

25:20.937 --> 25:23.105
- I WANT TO WATCH STEVE HARVEY!
- I CALL--I WAS HERE FIRST.

25:23.105 --> 25:24.899
[toilet flushes]

25:24.899 --> 25:26.568
- THAT DOESN'T MATTER.
- YES, IT DOES.

25:26.568 --> 25:28.069
- NO, IT DOESN'T.
THAT HAS NOTHING--

25:28.069 --> 25:29.445
NOPE.

25:29.445 --> 25:32.073
[kids yelling]
- I WAS HERE FIRST.

25:32.073 --> 25:34.533
- HEY!
HEY, HEY, HEY!

25:34.533 --> 25:38.287
WELL, WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?
- WE'RE FRIENDS OF CARL.

25:39.706 --> 25:40.790
- OKAY, WHERE IS HE?

25:42.792 --> 25:44.919
- THERE?

25:44.919 --> 25:46.504
- GO GET YOUR OWN.

25:46.504 --> 25:48.881
GIVE ME IT!

25:48.881 --> 25:51.550
- IS THERE SOMETHING
ON THE BOTTOM TO BREAK MY FALL?

25:51.550 --> 25:53.094
- PROBABLY NOT.

25:53.094 --> 25:55.304
- COOL.

25:57.390 --> 25:59.643
- YO, GET HER OUT OF THERE.
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

25:59.643 --> 26:00.644
- IS THAT YOUR DAD?

26:00.644 --> 26:04.021
- NO.

26:04.021 --> 26:05.690
- WHO THE FUCK
ARE THOSE KIDS DOWNSTAIRS?

26:05.690 --> 26:07.734
- THEY LIVE IN A VAN.
- WHY IS THAT MY PROBLEM?

26:07.734 --> 26:09.568
- IT'S THE WINTER.

26:09.568 --> 26:11.404
- [sighs]

26:11.404 --> 26:13.698
JUST GET RID OF THEM, OKAY?

26:13.698 --> 26:15.741
[knock at door]

26:15.741 --> 26:17.660
NO, ON SECOND THOUGHT,
THEY CAN STAY.

26:17.660 --> 26:18.995
- COOL.
- JUST TILL AFTER DINNER.

26:18.995 --> 26:20.579
THEN THEY'RE GONE.

26:21.998 --> 26:23.666
ALL RIGHT.

26:23.666 --> 26:25.710
- GIVE IT!
- NO!

26:25.710 --> 26:27.628
THIS IS MY REMOTE!
GET YOUR OWN!

26:27.628 --> 26:29.296
- NO!
- GIVE IT!

26:29.296 --> 26:30.673
- UH, PLAY.
UH, BE LOUD.

26:30.673 --> 26:32.634
JUST DO WHATEVER THE FUCK
YOU WANT, OKAY?

26:32.634 --> 26:33.718
all: YAY!

26:33.718 --> 26:34.719
- ALL RIGHT!

26:34.719 --> 26:36.512
[kids laughing and yelling]

26:36.512 --> 26:38.389
- DON'T HIT ME WITH THE BALL!

26:38.389 --> 26:40.516
YOU WITH THE BALL!

26:40.516 --> 26:44.061
DON'T EVER HIT ME WITH THE BALL!

26:44.061 --> 26:45.730
- WELCOME.

26:45.730 --> 26:48.024
- HELLO, I'M WESLEY GRETSKY
FROM DCFS.

26:48.024 --> 26:50.443
- OH.

26:50.443 --> 26:51.777
SHIT, SORRY.

26:51.777 --> 26:53.655
UH, THE--THE SOCIAL WORKER,
RIGHT?

26:53.655 --> 26:55.239
YEAH, WE'VE, UH...
WE'VE BEEN EXPECTING YOU.

26:55.239 --> 26:57.826
- I'D LIKE TO COME IN, PLEASE,
DO AN INSPECTION.

26:57.826 --> 26:59.118
- RIGHT, OKAY.
YEAH.

26:59.118 --> 27:01.454
UM, HEY, LISTEN,
IS THERE ANY CHANCE

27:01.454 --> 27:02.663
IN RESCHEDULING, YOU THINK??

27:02.663 --> 27:03.831
- WOULDN'T BE A SURPRISE VISIT

27:03.831 --> 27:05.291
IF WE RESCHEDULED,
NOW, WOULD IT?

27:05.291 --> 27:07.293
- NO.
NO, I GUESS NOT.

27:07.293 --> 27:09.754
[kids yelling]

27:09.754 --> 27:10.755
YEAH.

27:10.755 --> 27:12.506
- GO GET YOUR OWN.
WATCH UPSTAIRS.

27:12.506 --> 27:14.133
- GIVE IT!

27:18.679 --> 27:21.808
- FORM TWO LINES, PLEASE.

27:21.808 --> 27:22.933
- ALL RIGHT,
WHEN I CALL YOUR NAME,

27:22.933 --> 27:24.852
STEP UP AND GET
YOUR BUNK ASSIGNMENT.

27:24.852 --> 27:27.521
MELNICK, AUDREY.

27:27.521 --> 27:29.774
BED 32.

27:29.774 --> 27:33.235
GALLAGHER, FIONA.

27:33.235 --> 27:34.821
BED 44.

27:34.821 --> 27:35.821
- THANK YOU.
- DON'T THANK ME YET.

27:35.821 --> 27:37.156
YOU AIN'T TRIED
THE BED YET.

27:37.156 --> 27:41.035
[women jeering]

27:41.035 --> 27:42.871
- GOT SOME BROWN
ON YOUR NOSE, BITCH.

27:42.871 --> 27:44.955
- LONGFELD, JENNIFER.

27:44.955 --> 27:46.832
BED 35.

27:46.832 --> 27:48.667
[bluesy music]

27:48.667 --> 27:49.752
♪ ♪

27:49.752 --> 27:52.505
ROBERTS, TANESHA.
BED 36.

27:52.505 --> 27:56.717
♪ ♪

27:56.717 --> 27:58.344
- YOU CAN FUCKING EAT MY ASS,
CUNT.

27:58.344 --> 28:00.846
I TELL YOU ONE MORE TIME--

28:00.846 --> 28:02.515
- GET THE FUCK OUT OF MY FACE.
- DIRTY ASS DICK.

28:02.515 --> 28:03.933
MOVE! NOW!

28:07.603 --> 28:08.938
WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU LOOKING AT?

28:08.938 --> 28:10.731
- NOTHING.

28:10.731 --> 28:13.484
♪ ♪

28:13.484 --> 28:15.236
- WHY AM I HERE, MOMMY?

28:15.236 --> 28:17.404
- OH, HONEY, I TOLD YOU.

28:17.404 --> 28:19.907
YOU HAD AN ACCIDENT, REMEMBER?

28:19.907 --> 28:22.493
BUT THE DOCTORS
MADE YOU ALL BETTER.

28:22.493 --> 28:24.871
- WELL, THEN WE SHOULD GO.

28:24.871 --> 28:26.997
DADDY'S GONNA BE MAD
WE'RE NOT HOME TO MAKE DINNER.

28:26.997 --> 28:30.459
- NO, HE'LL UNDERSTAND.

28:30.459 --> 28:33.129
- SORRY, FOLKS.
VISITING HOURS ARE OVER.

28:33.129 --> 28:35.548
- OH, OKAY.

28:38.509 --> 28:39.844
- NIGHT, POPS.

28:39.844 --> 28:42.012
BE BACK FIRST THING
IN THE MORNING.

28:42.012 --> 28:43.180
- GOOD-BYE, DEB.

28:45.850 --> 28:48.102
- GOOD-BYE,
MY SWEET, SEXY MAN.

28:50.104 --> 28:51.647
- MOM, STOP.

28:51.647 --> 28:53.357
WE'RE IN PUBLIC.

28:53.357 --> 28:55.902
- OH, THAT'S RIGHT.
I FORGOT I'M MOM.

28:55.902 --> 28:57.194
- WAIT TILL WE GET HOME.

29:02.616 --> 29:04.660
- THESE NEED TO BE STORED
PROPERLY,

29:04.660 --> 29:06.620
WITH CAPS ON THEM.

29:06.620 --> 29:08.122
- AH, STUFF'S SO DILUTED,
I MEAN,

29:08.122 --> 29:10.875
I DOUBT THERE'S EVEN
ANY CLEANING PRODUCT LEFT.

29:10.875 --> 29:13.752
- A LOCKED CABINET
WOULD ALSO WORK.

29:18.757 --> 29:20.634
NEED A FIRE ALARM UP THERE,

29:20.634 --> 29:22.887
AS WELL AS A CO2 DETECTOR.
- OKAY.

29:28.684 --> 29:30.769
FLOORBOARD IS COMING UP
ON THIS STEP.

29:30.769 --> 29:33.147
COUPLE OF EXPOSED NAILS
ON THE ONE BELOW.

29:36.483 --> 29:38.611
[kids yelling]

29:38.611 --> 29:39.988
- HEY, UH, GUYS, YO!

29:39.988 --> 29:41.155
YOU THINK YOU COULD
KEEP IT DOWN?

29:41.155 --> 29:42.823
- YOU TOLD US WE COULD DO
WHATEVER WE WANT.

29:42.823 --> 29:43.991
- NOW I'M TELLING YOU
TO KEEP IT DOWN.

29:43.991 --> 29:45.409
- WHO ARE THESE CHILDREN?

29:45.409 --> 29:47.536
- UH, NEIGHBORHOOD KIDS.
I'M BABYSITTING.

29:47.536 --> 29:49.121
- SIX CHILDREN OR MORE
IS CONSIDERED A DAY CARE...

29:49.121 --> 29:50.581
- OKAY.

29:50.581 --> 29:51.790
- FOR WHICH YOU WILL NEED
A LICENSE...

29:51.790 --> 29:52.917
- OKAY.

29:52.917 --> 29:54.543
- WHICH I DON'T IMAGINE
YOU HAVE.

29:54.543 --> 29:56.420
- UH, YOU--YOU'VE IMAGINED
CORRECTLY.

29:56.420 --> 29:57.839
- GET A LICENSE

29:57.839 --> 29:59.715
OR BABYSIT LESS KIDS.

29:59.715 --> 30:01.967
- UH, EXPOSED WIRES.
YEAH, I'M ON IT.

30:01.967 --> 30:05.638
- NOW FOR THE $24,000 QUESTION.
- YEAH.

30:05.638 --> 30:07.348
- WHERE ARE THE GUARDIANS
OF THIS HOUSEHOLD?

30:07.348 --> 30:09.808
I HAVE A FRANCIS
AND FIONA GALLAGHER,

30:09.808 --> 30:10.976
FATHER AND SISTER.

30:10.976 --> 30:12.686
- YEAH, THEY'RE AT WORK.

30:12.686 --> 30:15.272
- THEY PUT YOU IN CHARGE?
- THAT'S CORRECT.

30:15.272 --> 30:16.941
- WHAT IS YOUR RELATIONSHIP
TO THIS HOUSEHOLD?

30:16.941 --> 30:18.442
- MY RELATIONSHIP
TO THE HOUSEHOLD.

30:18.442 --> 30:19.693
I'M THE, UH...
THE ELDEST BROTHER.

30:19.693 --> 30:21.237
I'M--I'M 19.

30:21.237 --> 30:23.239
- SO, IF I WERE TO CALL
MR. AND MISS GALLAGHER,

30:23.239 --> 30:24.908
I'D FIND THEM BOTH AT WORK?

30:24.908 --> 30:26.200
- YEAH.

30:28.994 --> 30:32.081
- AMANDA'S HERE
WITH HER PARENTS.

30:32.081 --> 30:33.666
- THIS IS LIP.

30:33.666 --> 30:36.002
THESE ARE MY PARENTS,
JASON AND SHERYL.

30:36.002 --> 30:36.961
THEY'RE WHITE.

30:36.961 --> 30:38.045
- I CAN SEE THAT.

30:38.045 --> 30:39.713
HI, NICE TO MEET YOU.

30:39.713 --> 30:41.507
- I GUESS I NEVER TOLD YOU
I WAS ADOPTED, HUH?

30:41.507 --> 30:42.716
- NO.

30:42.716 --> 30:43.842
- WELL, THEY BOUGHT ME

30:43.842 --> 30:45.219
FROM A SUBIC BAY
WHOREHOUSE, SO...

30:45.219 --> 30:46.845
GO, NAVY.

30:46.845 --> 30:48.222
- AMANDA,
THAT'S OUR PRIVATE BUSINESS.

30:48.222 --> 30:49.974
- UH, NO, DON'T WORRY.

30:49.974 --> 30:51.016
YOU'RE RIGHT IN THE MIDDLE
OF OUR PRIVATE AFFAIRS.

30:51.016 --> 30:53.061
THAT'S, UH, WESLEY
FROM THE DCFS.

30:53.061 --> 30:55.229
SHE'S A SOCIAL WORKER
HERE ON A SURPRISE VISIT.

30:55.229 --> 30:58.066
- MAYBE SHE'S YOUR REAL MOM.
- AND THAT'S MY BROTHER CARL.

30:58.066 --> 31:01.277
THESE ARE HIS FRIENDS.
THEY LIVE IN A VAN.

31:01.277 --> 31:02.278
SO WHO'S READY FOR DINNER?

31:02.278 --> 31:03.696
kids:
ME!

31:03.696 --> 31:04.655
- EH?
GO ON!

31:04.655 --> 31:06.198
[kids cheering]

31:06.198 --> 31:07.157
COME ON.

31:12.788 --> 31:15.833
[monitor beeping]

31:19.921 --> 31:22.464
- FIONA?

31:22.464 --> 31:24.216
FIONA, YOU'RE AWAKE?

31:25.843 --> 31:27.053
FIONA?

31:30.932 --> 31:33.017
- ARE YOU TALKING TO ME?

31:34.518 --> 31:36.562
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

31:36.562 --> 31:39.523
- SLEEPING.

31:39.523 --> 31:41.358
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

31:41.358 --> 31:44.403
- NOT SLEEPING.

31:44.403 --> 31:47.281
- OH, I'M SORRY.

31:47.281 --> 31:51.035
- LET'S BE QUIET
SO WE DON'T WAKE UP MONICA.

31:51.035 --> 31:53.704
- MONICA?

31:55.123 --> 31:57.833
- I'M SORRY WE LEFT YOU
AND YOUR BROTHER

31:57.833 --> 32:00.002
IN WASHINGTON PARK
LAST NIGHT.

32:00.002 --> 32:02.838
- OH.

32:02.838 --> 32:05.091
- THE DEALER GAVE US A SAMPLE.

32:05.091 --> 32:06.425
[laughs]

32:06.425 --> 32:11.055
I FORGOT YOU AND LIP
WERE WAITING OUTSIDE.

32:11.055 --> 32:13.015
HOW MANY HOURS WAS THAT?

32:14.141 --> 32:16.560
YOU COULD'VE FROZEN TO DEATH.

32:16.560 --> 32:20.189
I PROMISE I'M GONNA BE
A BETTER DAD.

32:21.648 --> 32:23.817
- IT'S OKAY.

32:24.985 --> 32:26.612
- YOU MAD AT ME?

32:27.946 --> 32:30.074
- NO.

32:31.533 --> 32:32.826
- HEY...

32:38.166 --> 32:40.167
WANT ME TO TAKE YOU
TO CLAIRE'S TOMORROW,

32:40.167 --> 32:42.544
GET YOUR EARS PIERCED?

32:42.544 --> 32:45.173
- OKAY.

32:48.134 --> 32:51.053
- I'M GLAD YOU'RE HERE
WITH ME, FIONA.

32:51.053 --> 32:54.807
- ME TOO, DADDY.

33:04.150 --> 33:07.111
- SO THEN I PUMMELED
THEIR FUCKING FACE IN GOOD.

33:07.111 --> 33:08.821
- THAT'LL TEACH THE QUEERS

33:08.821 --> 33:10.906
TO TRY TO RAPE A MILKOVICH
IN THE PRISON, HUH?

33:10.906 --> 33:12.491
HUH?

33:12.491 --> 33:14.034
- SPEAKING OF QUEERS.

33:14.034 --> 33:15.953
- WHAT THE HELL
DO YOU THINK YOU'RE DOING?

33:15.953 --> 33:17.329
- I THOUGHT YOUR FATHER
SHOULD KNOW

33:17.329 --> 33:18.914
HE DIDN'T BEAT
ALL THE QUEER OUT OF YOU.

33:18.914 --> 33:20.499
REALLY GONNA KILL YOU
THIS TIME.

33:22.084 --> 33:24.420
- KEEP YOUR FUCKING MOUTH SHUT.

33:24.420 --> 33:26.547
- CAN I TALK TO YOU
FOR A SECOND?

33:26.547 --> 33:29.175
- YOU KNOW, YOUR LIFE
RIGHT HERE, RIGHT NOW

33:29.175 --> 33:31.009
IS AS GOOD
AS IT'S EVER GONNA GET.

33:31.009 --> 33:32.761
YOU GOT TO GO GET PLOWED
ALL DAY, YEAH,

33:32.761 --> 33:34.221
BUT YOU COME HOME
TO A ROOF OVER YOUR HEAD

33:34.221 --> 33:35.556
AND FOOD
IN YOUR FUCKING BELLY.

33:35.556 --> 33:37.057
FIVE YEARS FROM NOW,

33:37.057 --> 33:39.060
YOU'RE GONNA BE A USED-UP,
DRIED-UP OLD WHORE,

33:39.060 --> 33:42.396
SUCKING GUYS OFF ON THE SIDEWALK
FOR FIVE BUCKS A POP.

33:42.396 --> 33:44.022
I WOULDN'T FUCK THIS UP
IF I WERE YOU.

33:46.483 --> 33:48.235
HEY.

33:48.235 --> 33:49.987
- I JUST WANTED TO LET YOU KNOW
THAT I'M LEAVING.

33:49.987 --> 33:51.363
- OKAY, I'LL SEE YOU BACK
AT THE PLACE

33:51.363 --> 33:53.241
- NO, DON'T.

33:53.241 --> 33:54.366
WE'RE DONE.

33:54.366 --> 33:57.120
- WHAT THE FUCK
ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

33:57.120 --> 34:00.247
- I DON'T HAVE ANY INTEREST
IN BEING A MISTRESS ANYMORE.

34:00.247 --> 34:03.083
- JESUS CHRIST.
WHEN DID YOU GET SO DRAMATIC?

34:03.083 --> 34:05.836
- WHEN I REALIZED
WHAT A PUSSY YOU ARE.

34:05.836 --> 34:09.006
- SAY IT AGAIN,
I'M GONNA KICK YOUR FUCKING ASS.

34:09.006 --> 34:11.008
- COME ON.
COME ON, BIG GUY.

34:11.008 --> 34:13.094
YOU THINK
YOU'RE A TOUGH MAN, HUH?

34:13.094 --> 34:14.470
YOU'RE NOT.

34:14.470 --> 34:16.096
YOU'RE A COWARD.

34:18.432 --> 34:21.268
- FUCK YOU.
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

34:21.268 --> 34:22.269
- OH, I DO UNDERSTAND.

34:22.269 --> 34:23.770
I UNDERSTAND BETTER THAN ANYONE

34:23.770 --> 34:25.147
THAT YOU'RE AFRAID
OF YOUR FATHER.

34:25.147 --> 34:28.150
YOU'RE AFRAID OF YOUR WIFE.

34:28.150 --> 34:30.402
YOU'RE AFRAID TO BE
WHO YOU ARE.

34:34.406 --> 34:36.700
- WELL, GOOD.
LEAVE.

34:36.700 --> 34:38.160
WHAT THE HELL
DO I CARE, BITCH?

34:43.291 --> 34:44.541
FUCK.

34:51.174 --> 34:52.424
HEY!

34:52.424 --> 34:54.843
EXCUSE ME!

34:54.843 --> 34:56.970
CAN I GET EVERYBODY'S ATTENTION,
PLEASE?

34:56.970 --> 34:59.348
[music stops]

34:59.348 --> 35:01.517
I JUST WANT
EVERYBODY HERE TO KNOW

35:01.517 --> 35:03.393
I'M FUCKING GAY.

35:06.021 --> 35:08.065
A BIG OLD 'MO.

35:10.276 --> 35:12.611
I JUST THOUGHT EVERYBODY
SHOULD KNOW THAT.

35:18.242 --> 35:20.244
YOU HAPPY NOW?

35:21.119 --> 35:25.166
[music resumes]

35:30.212 --> 35:31.713
- [yelling]

35:31.713 --> 35:34.258
I'LL FUCKING KILL YOU!

35:34.258 --> 35:35.425
YOU SON OF A BITCH!

35:40.430 --> 35:41.473
OH!

35:41.473 --> 35:46.979
[indiscernible yelling]

35:49.106 --> 35:50.899
- BEEN WANTING TO DO THIS
FOREVER.

35:59.200 --> 36:00.576
OH, SHIT.

36:00.576 --> 36:02.536
[yelling]

36:05.747 --> 36:08.166
- OH, SHIT.

36:08.166 --> 36:10.210
I BETTER CALL THE COPS.

36:10.210 --> 36:13.297
HEY, HAND ME MY PHONE,
WOULD YOU?

36:37.821 --> 36:40.657
- IT'S COLD OUT HERE.
- I DON'T CARE.

36:40.657 --> 36:42.326
- I DON'T EITHER.

36:42.326 --> 36:44.328
[clears throat]

36:48.373 --> 36:50.251
I HEARD WHAT HAPPENED
AT SCHOOL TODAY.

36:50.251 --> 36:52.169
- WHAT, YOUR STUPID GIRLFRIEND
TELL YOU?

36:52.169 --> 36:55.339
- SHE'S NOT MY GIRLFRIEND
ANYMORE.

36:55.339 --> 36:56.965
I BROKE UP WITH HER
AFTER I SAW

36:56.965 --> 36:59.385
THE PICTURES SHE POSTED
TO FACEBOOK.

36:59.385 --> 37:01.304
- YOU MEAN LIKE THESE ONES?

37:03.138 --> 37:04.681
- I THINK YOU LOOK PRETTY.

37:04.681 --> 37:08.143
- I'M THE LAUGHINGSTOCK
OF THE SEVENTH AND EIGHTH GRADE,

37:08.143 --> 37:09.895
MAYBE EVEN THE NINTH TOO.

37:09.895 --> 37:11.730
- YEAH, THERE ARE LOTS OF POSTS
THAT ARE "TEAM DEBBIE."

37:11.730 --> 37:13.357
- YOU MEAN LIKE THIS ONE?

37:13.357 --> 37:16.485
"NICE TITTIES.
WHERE'S MY MICROSCOPE?"

37:16.485 --> 37:18.320
- IT'LL BLOW OVER.

37:20.572 --> 37:22.783
- I THOUGHT HE LIKED ME.

37:22.783 --> 37:24.660
HE ASKED ME TO THE DANCE.

37:26.370 --> 37:28.872
- BOYS ARE...

37:28.872 --> 37:30.291
JACKASSES.

37:30.291 --> 37:33.294
- HE GAVE ME A FROG HEART.

37:33.294 --> 37:34.670
- HE WHAT?

37:36.380 --> 37:38.173
- I SUCK AT LOVE.

37:38.173 --> 37:40.842
- YEAH, TELL ME ABOUT IT.
I DATED SEEMA.

37:40.842 --> 37:43.011
- WHAT DID YOU LIKE ABOUT HER?

37:43.011 --> 37:46.473
- SHE SEEMED NICE.

37:46.473 --> 37:49.393
- SHE WASN'T.

37:49.393 --> 37:53.939
- YEAH, WELL,
GIRLS ARE SNEAKY.

37:53.939 --> 37:57.484
THEY NEVER REALLY SHOW YOU
THEIR TRUE COLORS.

37:57.484 --> 38:00.237
- I WAS MEAN
TO HER TOO, THOUGH.

38:00.237 --> 38:02.823
- YEAH, BUT YOU'RE THE KID.
SHE'S THE ADULT.

38:02.823 --> 38:03.490
SHE SHOULD'VE KNOWN BETTER.

38:03.490 --> 38:07.077
- I'M NOT A KID.

38:23.802 --> 38:25.429
- I'LL TAKE YOU TO THE DANCE.

38:27.013 --> 38:28.223
- REALLY?

38:28.223 --> 38:29.725
- MM-HMM.

38:29.725 --> 38:32.436
- YOU WON'T BE EMBARRASSED
TO BE SEEN WITH ME?

38:32.436 --> 38:35.439
- NO. NO.

38:35.439 --> 38:37.441
NO, I'LL BE PROUD.

38:37.441 --> 38:40.444
[mellow rock music]

38:40.444 --> 38:47.451
♪ ♪

38:47.451 --> 38:50.454
[men yelling]

38:54.958 --> 38:56.377
- FUCKING FAGGOT!

38:56.377 --> 38:57.544
GET OUT OF MY HOUSE!

38:57.544 --> 38:59.087
YOU POLE-SMOKING QUEER!

38:59.087 --> 39:00.797
- FUCK YOU!
DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT!

39:00.797 --> 39:02.090
I'VE BEEN STAYING AT IAN'S

39:02.090 --> 39:03.508
SINCE YOU'VE BEEN
IN THE CAN, BITCH!

39:03.508 --> 39:05.260
GUESS WHAT
WE'VE BEEN DOING, DADDY!

39:05.260 --> 39:06.428
WE'VE BEEN FUCKING!

39:06.428 --> 39:07.888
AND I TAKE IT!

39:07.888 --> 39:10.015
HE GIVES IT TO ME
GOOD AND HARD,

39:10.015 --> 39:11.517
AND I FUCKING LIKE IT.

39:11.517 --> 39:12.642
[spits]

39:12.642 --> 39:14.437
- LET ME GO!
- CALM DOWN, TERRY.

39:14.437 --> 39:15.479
- FUCK YOU!

39:15.479 --> 39:16.521
I SUCK HIS DICK.

39:16.521 --> 39:18.064
I FUCKING LOVE IT.

39:18.064 --> 39:19.107
- GET HIM OUT OF HERE!

39:19.107 --> 39:20.442
- FUCK YOU!

39:20.442 --> 39:21.818
- I'M GONNA CUT YOUR BALLS
IN LITTLE PIECES

39:21.818 --> 39:23.028
AND SHOVE THEM
UP YOUR ASS SO FAR,

39:23.028 --> 39:25.155
YOU GROW BALL TREES, YOU FUCK.

39:25.155 --> 39:26.740
[grunts]

39:26.740 --> 39:28.575
- WHAT IS YOUR PROBLEM, TERRY?

39:28.575 --> 39:31.536
YOU BEEN OUT FOR FOUR HOURS,
AND YOU'RE ALREADY INTO A FIGHT?

39:31.536 --> 39:34.498
YOU'RE BREAKING
YOUR PROBATION.

39:34.498 --> 39:37.250
- FUCKERS!
FUCKERS!

39:38.627 --> 39:40.253
- AND AS FOR YOU...

39:42.506 --> 39:44.299
YOU'RE FREE TO GO.

39:44.299 --> 39:46.134
- WHAT?

39:46.134 --> 39:48.553
- IF I ARREST YOU, IT'S GONNA BE
A LOT OF PAPERWORK.

39:48.553 --> 39:50.180
KEEP ME IN THE OFFICE
ALL NIGHT.

39:50.180 --> 39:53.266
I'D RATHER GET HOME
TO MY HUSBAND, CARLOS.

39:55.018 --> 39:56.812
[siren blips]

39:59.773 --> 40:01.149
- ME AND BONNIE ARE FINISHED.

40:01.149 --> 40:02.400
WE'RE HEADING UPSTAIRS.

40:02.400 --> 40:04.861
- ALL RIGHT.
EMAIL YOUR SISTER, YEAH?

40:04.861 --> 40:06.363
- OH, LIP'S SISTER'S IN PRISON.

40:06.363 --> 40:07.490
- NO WAY.

40:07.490 --> 40:08.616
OUR AUNTIE'S IN PRISON TOO.

40:08.616 --> 40:10.033
- SHE IS? FOR WHAT?

40:10.033 --> 40:11.952
- MURDER.
SHE'S ON DEATH ROW.

40:14.037 --> 40:16.832
- WHY--WHY IS YOUR SISTER
IN PRISON?

40:16.832 --> 40:18.416
- UH, WELL, THE FIRST TIME

40:18.416 --> 40:20.836
WAS FOR ALMOST KILLING
LIAM HERE WITH COCAINE,

40:20.836 --> 40:23.213
AND, UH--AND THEN
THE SECOND TIME

40:23.213 --> 40:25.006
WAS FOR BREAKING PROBATION

40:25.006 --> 40:26.883
AND GOING OUT WITH THE GUY
WHO GAVE HER COCAINE.

40:26.883 --> 40:30.303
- MY, YOU--YOU HAVE
QUITE A COLORFUL STORY.

40:31.596 --> 40:34.517
- THAT'S A NICE WAY
OF PUTTING IT.

40:34.517 --> 40:36.184
YOU DON'T LIKE YOUR DINNER?

40:36.184 --> 40:37.894
- OH, WE HAD A LATE LUNCH.

40:37.894 --> 40:40.438
- OKAY, IF YOU DON'T MIND,
I'M JUST GONNA...

40:40.438 --> 40:41.398
EXCUSE ME.

40:45.528 --> 40:49.657
UM, IF YOU'RE HUNGRY.

40:49.657 --> 40:51.241
IT'S NOT VERY GOOD.

40:53.493 --> 40:55.954
- SO ALL THOSE KIDS
LIVE IN A VAN?

40:55.954 --> 40:57.122
- UH, YEAH.
YEAH, APPARENTLY.

40:57.122 --> 40:58.248
[clears throat]

40:58.248 --> 41:00.041
- AND YOU'RE WATCHING THEM?

41:00.041 --> 41:03.295
- WELL, YEAH,
VANS ARE, UH, COLD,

41:03.295 --> 41:04.588
YOU KNOW, CROWDED.

41:06.339 --> 41:08.884
- MOST PEOPLE I SEE
ARE TRYING TO DUMP THEIR KIDS,

41:08.884 --> 41:10.552
NOT COLLECT MORE.

41:10.552 --> 41:13.639
- YOU KNOW, NEIGHBORHOOD'S
GOT TO STICK TOGETHER.

41:14.556 --> 41:17.225
- THERE YOU GO.

41:17.225 --> 41:19.603
AND IT LOOKS LIKE
MY NEXT SURPRISE VISIT HERE

41:19.603 --> 41:22.647
WILL BE IN TWO SATURDAYS
AT 4:00 P.M.

41:22.647 --> 41:24.608
HAVE A GOOD NIGHT.

41:24.608 --> 41:27.319
- OKAY.
UH, I'LL GET THAT.

41:30.822 --> 41:32.073
- HEY, YOUR GRADES ARE UP.

41:32.073 --> 41:33.659
- OH, YEAH, I SAW.

41:33.659 --> 41:34.826
"C" IN ENGLISH.

41:34.826 --> 41:36.036
I'M GONNA LOSE
MY SCHOLARSHIP

41:36.036 --> 41:37.538
AND HAVE TO DROP OUT
OF SCHOOL.

41:37.538 --> 41:39.080
- OH, THAT'S TOO BAD.

41:39.080 --> 41:41.584
- UNLESS YOU GOT AN "A"
IN MACRO AND PHILOSOPHY

41:41.584 --> 41:43.501
AND A "B" IN THERMO.

41:43.501 --> 41:45.045
- WHAT?
LET ME SEE THAT.

41:48.548 --> 41:50.091
HOLY SHIT.

41:50.091 --> 41:51.593
THAT'S FANTASTIC.

41:59.517 --> 42:01.519
- SMILE.

42:01.519 --> 42:05.566
[camera shutter clicks]

42:05.566 --> 42:06.900
COOL.

42:08.360 --> 42:10.278
- TELLING YOUR SISTER
ABOUT ME?

42:10.278 --> 42:15.283
- "I'M IN YOUR BED
WITH MY GIRLFRIEND, BONNIE.

42:15.283 --> 42:16.826
"STAY IN PRISON.

42:16.826 --> 42:18.495
LOVE, CARL."

42:18.495 --> 42:21.539
[tender rock music]

42:21.539 --> 42:26.670
♪ ♪

42:26.670 --> 42:30.633
- I DON'T LIKE SEX.

42:30.633 --> 42:32.133
- OH.

42:36.262 --> 42:39.975
- BUT WE CAN STILL KISS
AND STUFF IF YOU WANT.

42:39.975 --> 42:42.435
- YEAH, I LIKE THIS.

42:42.435 --> 42:43.728
- ME TOO.

42:43.728 --> 42:49.610
♪ ♪

42:49.610 --> 42:52.738
- THIS IS NOT THE ENVIRONMENT
THAT I WANT FOR MY DAUGHTER.

42:52.738 --> 42:54.489
- JASON, WHAT HAPPENED?

42:54.489 --> 42:57.659
- THERE IS A CHILD WHO ALMOST
ATE HIS OWN FECES OUT THERE.

42:57.659 --> 43:00.120
- OH, SHIT, GUESS HE DIDN'T GET
ENOUGH DINNER.

43:00.120 --> 43:01.997
- I'D LIKE YOU TO STOP
SEEING AMANDA.

43:01.997 --> 43:04.541
- IT'S KIND OF NOT
YOUR CHOICE.

43:04.541 --> 43:05.626
- HOW MUCH?

43:05.626 --> 43:08.294
- HOW MUCH WHAT?

43:08.294 --> 43:09.797
- JASON, DON'T.

43:09.797 --> 43:11.423
- WHY, BECAUSE YOU WANT HER
TO BE WITH HIM?

43:11.423 --> 43:12.966
- SHE'S AN ADULT.

43:12.966 --> 43:14.968
- YEAH, SHE'S AN ADULT
WHO I'M SUPPORTING.

43:14.968 --> 43:16.970
HOW MUCH TO STOP DATING HER?
- EXCUSE ME?

43:16.970 --> 43:18.722
- YOU KNOW, SHE'S NOT
IN LOVE WITH YOU.

43:18.722 --> 43:20.015
YOU DO KNOW THAT, RIGHT?

43:20.015 --> 43:21.599
- WE'RE NOT REALLY
AT THAT STAGE YET.

43:21.599 --> 43:22.726
- SHE'S JUST TRYING
TO DRIVE ME CRAZY

43:22.726 --> 43:24.436
BY GOING OUT
WITH SOMEONE LIKE YOU.

43:24.436 --> 43:25.854
- SOMEONE LIKE ME?
- YEAH.

43:25.854 --> 43:27.648
I MEAN, YOU SEEM
LIKE A PERFECTLY NICE KID,

43:27.648 --> 43:29.065
BUT AMANDA'S JUST REBELLING.

43:29.065 --> 43:30.483
- WELL, DON'T BLAME HER.

43:30.483 --> 43:31.985
YOU'RE KIND OF A DICK.

43:31.985 --> 43:35.155
- I'M NOT DENYING THAT.

43:35.155 --> 43:38.408
HOW ABOUT $5,000, THEN?

43:38.408 --> 43:41.161
LOOKS LIKE THAT WOULD GO
PRETTY FAR IN THIS PLACE.

43:41.161 --> 43:42.620
- JASON.
- IS HE SERIOUS?

43:42.620 --> 43:45.373
HE'S GONNA PAY ME
NOT TO DATE YOUR DAUGHTER?

43:45.373 --> 43:47.375
- HOW ABOUT $10,000?

43:47.375 --> 43:48.836
I HAVE THE CASH
WITH ME.

43:48.836 --> 43:51.337
- ON YOU,
IN THIS NEIGHBORHOOD?

43:51.337 --> 43:53.799
- HAVE WE GOT A DEAL?

44:03.266 --> 44:04.726
- [groans]

44:15.570 --> 44:18.073
HEY, FIONA.

44:18.073 --> 44:20.033
YOU HUNGRY?

44:20.033 --> 44:23.578
I'M GONNA GO GET US
SOMETHING TO EAT.

44:23.578 --> 44:24.996
OH, GOD.

44:30.668 --> 44:32.670
AH, JEEZ!

44:39.511 --> 44:42.305
- SO YOUR FATHER
JUST OFFERED ME 10 GRAND

44:42.305 --> 44:43.891
TO STAY AWAY FROM YOU.

44:43.891 --> 44:46.768
- AMANDA, YOU KNOW WE LOVE YOU.

44:46.768 --> 44:48.478
- DID YOU TAKE THE MONEY?

44:48.478 --> 44:50.146
- UH, WHAT DO YOU THINK?

44:50.146 --> 44:52.232
- THAT YOU DID.

44:52.232 --> 44:53.358
- REALLY?

44:53.358 --> 44:54.859
- WELL, DID YOU?

44:56.027 --> 44:57.028
- YEAH.

44:58.446 --> 45:01.282
- SO WE'RE BREAKING UP, THEN?

45:01.282 --> 45:03.869
- WELL, A DEAL'S A DEAL, RIGHT?

45:03.869 --> 45:06.538
- OKAY, AMANDA, COME.
WE'RE LEAVING.

45:06.538 --> 45:08.832
- LOOK, YOU TAUGHT ME
TO BE A MAN OF MY WORD.

45:08.832 --> 45:12.544
- AND I WAS JUST STARTING
TO REALLY LIKE YOU.

45:18.550 --> 45:21.511
[upbeat rock music]

45:21.511 --> 45:29.561
♪ ♪

46:08.600 --> 46:10.853
[knock at door]

46:19.861 --> 46:20.862
- HEY.

46:23.824 --> 46:24.991
OW!
- 10 GRAND?

46:24.991 --> 46:26.534
- I PANICKED.

46:26.534 --> 46:27.911
- I TOLD YOU HE GAVE
MY BMX BOYFRIEND

46:27.911 --> 46:29.746
IN HIGH SCHOOL
$15,000.

46:29.746 --> 46:31.789
- I DIDN'T KNOW HE WAS GONNA
HAVE THE CASH ON HIM.

46:31.789 --> 46:34.042
- YOU SHOULD'VE HELD OUT.

46:34.042 --> 46:36.962
- I'D NEVER SEEN
THAT MUCH MONEY BEFORE.

46:38.504 --> 46:41.507
[spunky rock music]

46:41.507 --> 46:49.224
♪ ♪

46:52.602 --> 46:54.604
- [sighs]

46:57.065 --> 46:58.566
GAY, HUH?

47:06.616 --> 47:09.535
- I THINK I BROKE
HALF A FUCKING TOOTH.

47:09.535 --> 47:11.746
- YEAH, MY RIBS
DON'T FEEL SO GOOD.

47:16.084 --> 47:18.169
SO YOU REALLY CAME OUT, HUH?

47:18.169 --> 47:20.463
- DOESN'T MEAN I'M GONNA WEAR
A FUCKING DRESS OR ANYTHING.

47:20.463 --> 47:22.590
- NOBODY FUCKING ASKED YOU TO.

47:24.968 --> 47:26.928
THOUGH YOU DO HAVE
REALLY NICE LEGS.

47:29.847 --> 47:31.349
- YOU'RE A FUCKING DICK.

47:31.349 --> 47:33.559
[both laughing]

47:33.559 --> 47:35.353
YEAH, THERE.

47:35.353 --> 47:36.980
THAT'S WHAT YOU GET.

47:36.980 --> 47:38.064
[laughs]

47:43.904 --> 47:46.907
[Portugal. The Man's
Sleep Forever]

47:46.907 --> 47:54.998
♪ ♪

47:55.832 --> 47:58.376
- ALL RIGHT, I'M CALLING IT.

47:58.376 --> 48:00.753
MARK THE TIME OF DEATH,
9:05.

48:00.753 --> 48:03.966
[sustained beep]

48:05.383 --> 48:07.051
- NO!

48:07.051 --> 48:11.973
♪ ♪

48:11.973 --> 48:14.017
FIONA.

48:14.017 --> 48:22.025
♪ ♪
